snippet.title: Carnivores: Dinosaur Hunter HD reveal trailer
snippet.description:
A classic best-selling dinosaur hunting simulator Carnivores is back as a completely new experience!

Carnivores: Dinosaur Hunter HD is a brand new game for PlayStation 3 set in the same universe and featuring recognizable dinosaur types, familiar weapons and equipment. The game provides similar experience to any hunting simulators: you have to stalk your prey using tracking devices, scent maskers and quail calls. Yet it is far from your average deer hunter: going against the largest creatures known to mankind, you will need all your skills to survive. Hunt or be hunted!

www.carnivores-hd.com

music used:
From Ashes by Matthias H. Benz
https://soundcloud.com/matthias-h-benz/from-ashes
